      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CRACKERJACK RALF (3) was in winning form two back (25.45) at Warrnambool but ran below best last time at Sandown, finishing 8th. Solid record here at the distance winning two races. Comes out of a solid form race last start. Better than the latest effort and deserves another chance. BAROOGA JIM (7) has a strong record this trip with eight wins and seven placings from 21 starts. Missed the frame latest (26.12) when seventh over 460m at Geelong in a Grade 4/5. Looks one of the chances. GIACOMO (1) has a strong record this trip with eight wins and four placings from 21 starts. Was out of placings last time (30.04) at Sandown in a Free For All, finishing fourth and beaten 8 lengths. Can feature with the right run. ULTIMATE WARRIOR (4) is always hard to beat when he races at this trip.",
